Author: garbonzogod
Text: I guess normal people just see weight loss as a positive. Hearing things like that just makes me want to restrict harder. I hope you can get through the holidays without problems :( holidays are rough.

Author: VampFag88
Text: I did the same thing.  They're not very supportive.  I even skipped Thanksgiving this year and they still don't see that I am having issues.
